Lil Wayne's 2011 mixtape Sorry 4 the Wait was released as a sort of apology for Tha Carter IV's delay. Now, since Tha Carter V has been similarly pushed back thanks to an ongoing battle between Wayne and Birdman, he's delivered Sorry 4 the Wait 2.
